{"tid":670498,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Gaspar noe公開評論《black panther》","createTime":"2018-05-19T11:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T12:16:25.000Z","uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9281e2dcfb4f8cca9cd0c21636ba8f1a85dc3111","tid":670498,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:56:35.000Z","msg":"Marvel 超級英雄電影\u001c《Black Panther》無疑地在大眾市場上獲得莫大成功，不過，並非所有人都喜歡這部電影，其中也包括了以《Climax》獲得了第 50 屆坎城影展會外賽「導演雙週」的藝術電影獎得主 &ndash; Gaspar Noe。近日 Gaspar Noe 接受 Variety 訪問時公開評論了《Black Panther》，他在訪問中表示：「我試著看這部電影，但是看了 20 分鐘我不得不逃離電影院，《Black Panther》跟《Star Wars》一樣爛，我討厭《Star Wars》也討厭 R&amp;B！」除此之外，Gaspar Noe 也表示自己最喜歡的是紀錄片類型的電影，因為這類的電影可以讓觀眾從中學到非常多事。他直言劇情太容易被預測到的喜劇、動作電影、科幻電影往往引不起他的興趣，甚至多半覺得無聊。Gaspar Noe 語出驚人，不曉得各位又是如何看待呢？"},{"pid":"febf28d38b5eb3597ed8a9d0e82ab6a0e864bb52","tid":670498,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/hb1hptq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2Fhb1hptq&d=F%2Fo2CmL55g%2FmPkxraNtbaEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=7bcca1ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/hb1hptq</a>"},{"pid":"fc05363d10eaa3a9d29064fa496750ebce5f5399","tid":670498,"uid":63588,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"黑豹劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/19/201205_0fad85419b83cd30785c350ea44905d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F19%2F201205_0fad85419b83cd30785c350ea44905d6.png&h=45decd77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da3dd6292f00e3f08f46908f80c72ec9d0c40156","tid":670498,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc05363d10eaa3a9d29064fa496750ebce5f5399","tid":670498,"uid":63588,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"黑豹劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.